Akeeba Subscriptions 4.2.0
================================================================================
+ Add a new plugin to conform to EU regulations regarding VAT and notification of the withdrawal period
+ gh-86 Allow spaces in usernames for Joomla! 3.3 and later
+ gh-90 Record the user's IP address on subscription (also the country, if you have the GeoIP plugin installed)
+ gh-91 Show tax-inclusive prices in the front-end, allowing the client to select their country
+ gh-88 Show the tax rate in the sign-up page
# [LOW] PayPal IPN could fail if User-Agent is not set (thanks, Vic!)
# [LOW] gh-82 The expiration by week report wouldn't work on live sites due to the wrong loading order of Javascript files.
# [LOW] Subscription options: value cut off in locales using commas as decimal separators

Akeeba Subscriptions 4.1.2
================================================================================
+ New message tags: [SLUG], [RENEWALURL] and [RENEWALURL:YourCouponCodeHere]
~ Updated .htaccess files for Apache 2.4 compatibility
